commit.message:
Replace Ruby license with MIT LICENSE.txt (#10)

Previously the Ruby license was specified in the readme and in the gem, but the MIT license was declared in the gemspec. I've moved entirely to the much more common, and already declared MIT license to prevent any confusion for users of this gem.
